  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Non smokers

          -  Able to adhere to study visits and protocol requirements

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any clinical safety laboratory measurements value &gt; Grade 1 on WHO Toxicity Scale

          -  Established or recurrent history of allergic reactions
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
